          "title": "BLOBSPACE 101",
          "summary": "Proto-danksharding, or EIP-4844, is coming to Ethereum soon to address scalability issues. It introduces a concept called blobspace, which can reduce transaction costs by simplifying the data commitment process. Blobspace helps to verify that all transaction information is available for block validation without every node needing to download all data, making the process more efficient. This upgrade will particularly benefit L2 solutions like rollups.",
